---
name: Chalkboard
description: Style preset — Chalkboard
tags: [style, retro, aspect-16:9]
---
Render as if drawn on a classic green chalkboard with a dark green chalkboard-textured background with subtle chalk dust. Use white and colored chalk (yellow, pink, light blue) for all lines, shapes, and text. The lettering should look like clean chalk handwriting. Add subtle smudge effects and chalk texture to lines. The result should feel like a beautifully organized lecture -- academic, warm, and intellectual.
